description:
When you think of Adventist identity, what words or thoughts come to mind?

Perhaps words like Sabbath, advent, and the health message come to mind.

On October 13th, scholars from around the world attended the Conference on Adventist Identity. Here they discussed important topics and doctrines regarding who Adventists are and what we stand for.

Learn more and find other Adventist news on adventist.news.
